1.0.name: wordpress/facebooktwittergoogle-plus-one-share-buttons
1.0.description:
Facebook Like, Twitter, Google +, Pinterest, Linkedin, Stumbleupon Buttons after post contents.

Features:

  • Smart Pinterest share, allows you to set the image or get the first image automatically

  • All buttons can show counts.

  • Show buttons after post contents by default.(See FAQs-2 for how to show buttons elsewhere)

For more information,refer to Facebook,Twitter,Google plus one Share Buttons Doc
